:07.000Z","msg":"我以前會行鼠先...優先解決人地隻象"},{"pid":"db0b602b6bffd1c0902f7ab4bd203a918cb21e9b","tid":290070,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T15:58:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我以前會行鼠先...優先解決人地隻象</blockquote><br />\n但係都係好難食到<br />\n隻象隔離太多保鑣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"985a73a29a90091a40cb304bde07bd26a69fe829","tid":290070,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T17:46:10.000Z","msg":"鼠一進一"},{"pid":"7ad19535131923dbc5dca2bc7d20a83ccd9bd616","tid":290070,"uid":2795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T17:48:56.000Z","msg":"老鼠係咪唔可以上岸個下即刻食對面隻象<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b4bbe136f632a4bcf2e2d23433f9321dd8770ba","tid":290070,"uid":52468,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T19:24:36.000Z","msg":"唔記得點挽已經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c577ea9744b04db8bbff800ae243c7edebb1efa","tid":290070,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T21:54:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔記得點挽已經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">挽</span></span>"},{"pid":"bd10cadc951a5c696382f3c33be92d4682e01d4d","tid":290070,"uid":26084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T22:02:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>香港人拎中國旅行證，通常係因為唔見左特區護照而拎。中國旅行證等同嗰本係中國護照，並唔係香港護照。<br />\n<br />\n用中國旅行證冇拎簽證入境其他國家的話，會好大機會比人控告非法入境。<br />\n<br />\n你有冇拎過bno？有的話建議你在英國直接申請一本，冇舊嗰本的話，要填多張form declare lost，4-6星期就有。可以加錢加急，2星期。亦可以再加多d錢預約做特急，即日。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n補充一點，佢等同中國護照，但所有免簽待遇不適用，所以去「所有」國家係要另外申請簽證。<br />\n<br />\n如果你冇資格申請bno，我建議你立即去印尼駐英國領事館申請旅遊簽證。</blockquote><br />\n唔該晒巴打，仲諗住有一絲希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你係長住英國？<br />\n<br />\n有希望嘅，申請印尼visa都唔困難啊，幾日應該有<br />\n<br />\n而且，你如果以前有曾經拎過bno嘅話，咁申請左bno就可以完全取替特區護照，去邊都唔係問題啦。</blockquote><br />\n今年final啦<br />\n就係父母無幫我申請過bno<br />\n如果唔係現家都唔洗咁煩<br />\n打過去印尼駐英國領事館啦，佢話travel document唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幾時去印尼？7月中底去的話都有機，特區護照提供海外申請。<br />\n<br />\nBno 的話，有可能申請過忘記左或者唔知道遮，你睇睇你身分證左下角括號日期係幾多？</blockquote><br />\n我今晚機啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同咪下個星期機票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見最多都要兩星期先有hk passport<br />\n你講身份證號碼個括號定咩？<br />\n一個括號係8一個係01-05<br />\n我問左好多次父母都話無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw多謝你熱心既幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n今晚機去bali<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？oh... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nsosad...<br />\n<br />\n下星期機票回港嘛？咁真係幫唔到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n01-05 咁真係冇bno了⋯⋯</blockquote><br />\n果個日期唔係兒童新份證日期咩"},{"pid":"1fd6af5a08aa24ad2562ccf04b6307a7e0bec345","tid":290070,"uid":14539,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T22:05:18.000Z","msg":"以前小學玩 中間四隻會退落一格"},{"pid":"176ec36471e8875973973401c3fadcd10d86c1e7","tid":290070,"uid":18265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T22:55:23.000Z","msg":"上鼠/落狼/郁獅/"},{"pid":"7fffba113c713a82d49d138c58eb0ce621506b1d","tid":290070,"uid":92682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T23:01:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔記得點挽已經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquo